<Base title="Committee Mandate & Operations">
  <h1>Committee Mandate & Operations</h1>
  <h2>About the Commission</h2>
  <p>The Research Ethics Committee of the Institute of Informatics oversees the ethical conduct of all research activities carried out within the institute.</p>
  <h2>Powers of the Commission</h2>
  <p>The committee reviews research proposals, issues opinions, and monitors compliance with ethical standards throughout the research lifecycle.</p>
</Base>